Package: sapthesisdown
Title: An R Markdown version of the Sapthesis template using thesisdown and bookdown packages
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tullia", "Padellini", email = "tullia.padellini@uniroma1.it", role = "cre"),
    person("Francesco", "Biccari", email = "biccari@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Using the bookdown package and LaTeX and Word thesis templates from
    Reed College, this package aims to encourage reproducible research using
    simple Markdown syntax while embedding all of the R code to produce plots
    and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Tullia Padellini <tullia.padellini@uniroma1.it>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    devtools,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    thesisdown
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: pandoc (>= 1.18) - http://pandoc.org
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
